  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To address early vessel healing and thrombus formation after deployment of three distinct
      groups of stents
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A prospective, randomized study providing new evidences on early vessel healing and thrombus
      development after stenting with different devices.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
